{"tid":511013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"WhatsApp明年起 停止支援多款手機系統","createTime":"2017-12-27T05:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T12:35:25.000Z","uid":28366,"like":11,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e6b1ccf5b9814212e6189308a75b165671be2624","tid":511013,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T05:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171227/large/1514350148_8d4a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171227%2Flarge%2F1514350148_8d4a.png&h=19b6f543&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在香港相當流行的通訊軟件WhatsApp早前宣佈，將陸續不再為多款舊有手機系統提供支援，但限期一拖再拖，不過今次於終「無得拖」！包括BlackBerry、Windows Phone 8.0或之前的裝置，將於12月31日起不再受支援；而明年年底亦會停止支援Nokia S40；到2020年亦會停止支援Android 2.3.7或之前的裝置。<br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp稱，這些系統的原有用戶雖然可以繼續使用WhatsApp，但用家將不能再使用有關裝置建立新帳號或重新驗證原有帳號，而且不會積極地提供新功能，部份原有功能甚至會隨時停止運行。<br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp解釋，停止支援是因為這些裝置的作業系統無法配合將來功能發展的需求，建議受影響用戶在限期前升級至新的作業系統，或轉為使用Android OS 4.0+、iPhone iOS7+或Windows Phone 8.1+的手機。WhatsApp又提醒用戶，升級或轉用新裝置後只須在新機上安裝WhatsApp軟件和進行驗證，就能繼續使用原有的賬戶。<br />\n<br />\n不過，WhatsApp目前無法做到跨平台繼承對話，換言之若是使用Android作業系統的用戶，轉用至Windows Phone將無法載入原有對話記錄，只能透過電郵附件的方式傳送對話記錄至新系統。<br />\n<br />\n【WhatsApp停止支援作業系統】<br />\n●BlackBerry 作業系統和 BlackBerry 10手機 （2017年12月31日之前）<br />\n●Windows Phone 8.0或之前的裝置（2017年12月31日之前）<br />\n●Nokia S40（2018年12月31日之前）<br />\n●Android 2.3.7和之前的系統版本裝置（2020年2月1日之前）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171227/57630821\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171227%2F57630821&d=hfWUNa6%2FVpXfuI8YhkX16p4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=bc19742f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171227%2F57630821&h=ade648d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171227/57630821</a>"},{"pid":"3c468e63e8be0a0c4fbfc8b9fdd2ba1efd894684","tid":511013,"uid":146917,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T05:11:15.000Z","msg":"理由合理"},{"pid":"157cbc6aebd44deba1a95f21a71925d1d2873021","tid":511013,"uid":53105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T05:13:04.000Z","msg":"fb<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9835d6c5722b4c1630b6768085d5b450f1985404","tid":511013,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T05:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a8ee5cbc8a03a0d433ec5851deeea3f6cdf94a","tid":511013,"uid":42804,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T05:32:29.000Z","msg":"大勢所趨。<br />\n黑莓早年已經轉行android系統以及將手機部判畀印度以及中國Tcl,自己搞網絡安全系統，bb10系統都係玩多一兩年就唔玩。<br />\nNokia重生後都行android，之前個啲s40系統真係唔多適合WhatsApp操作。<br />\nWM唔使講，少數民族。<br />\n而家一出街，唔係an機就iOS，再加上越出越平，都唔會有人仲用緊五年前嘅機，行五年前嘅系統。"},{"pid":"962ca9a3adfe8e93e711dfe6fc4b2d90b8f937cc","tid":511013,"uid":85819,"like":4,"dislike":134,"score":-130,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T05:34:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77d9fe0b29409716fb468d1c13a9a098f7d02d3b","tid":511013,"uid":14586,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"962ca9a3adfe8e93e711dfe6fc4b2d90b8f937cc","tid":511013,"uid":85819,"like":4,"dislike":134,"score":-130,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T05:34:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T05:35:41.000Z","msg":"Wechat<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"390eb43d0462ba39c725b0cf52bf43510d508129","tid":511013,"uid":35129,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T05:37:35.000Z","msg":"垃圾content farm<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90c51df4179ceeea87ce8b5f96cc04a9bef887e","tid":511013,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T05:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\